\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Why are some industries and/or firms so profitable? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How do strategic decisions fit together?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
When should the firm “buy or build”, e.g.
 fast “last mile” delivery?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How do we deter entrants? Not disturb large incumbents?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How do we cooperate with rivals and avoid jail, e.g.
 fare codes? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Why are so many recent “unicorn” startups exploiting network effects? How
 can we solve the chicken-and-egg problem? 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
